messages.content: You are an assistant that helps convert user questions to Cypher queries.
What are the top 5 products managed by the Haiti Field Office?

MATCH (o:Office{name: 'Haiti Field Office'})-[:MANAGED_BY]->(p:Product)
RETURN p
ORDER BY p.line_item_quantity DESC

Which vendors supply products to offices that manage more than 3 different types of product groups?

WITH v, o, count(DISTINCT pg) AS numProductGroups

RETURN DISTINCT v.name AS Vendor, o.name AS Office, numProductGroups as NumberOfProductGroups
